Method Detail

forAllEjbRefs

public void forAllEjbRefs(String template)
                   throws XDocletException
Process the tag body for each weblogic:ejb-reference-description tag in all source files. Please note that this tag already iterates over all available sources; it should not be enclosed by a <XDtClass:forAllClasses> tag or any other that process classes. This tag does not process tags with duplicated ejb-ref-name attributes. If such tags occurs, only the first tag is processed, and further tags will only emit a warning message.

Parameters:
template - The body of the block tag
Throws:
XDocletException - if something goes wrong
doc.tag
type="block"
